name: Colby Classic Skate Deck
description:
The first ever Colby Phillips drawn skate deck to go on the market, the Colby Classic is perfect for any die hard skater. Not only does it have killer artwork, but it helps Fight Hunger in Santa Cruz County and beyond.

This Special Edition skate deck comes in 1 size:

• 8.0

**100% of proceeds benefit Grind Out Hunger**

• 8.0

• 8.25
